Go To https://www.tenable.com/products/nessus

look for nessus essential

select download

get your free activation code

if your system has no support than get the download from teneble downloads.(download it just in case)

go to terminal and cd to downloads

run the command "sudo dpkg -i [package]

to start the program run "sudo systemctl start nessusd.service"

to check if the program in running run "sudo systemctl status nessusd.service"
